32:48.410 --> 32:51.370
INTO HOW THE KILLER AND YOUR WIFE MAY HAVE...

32:51.540 --> 32:53.530
FOUND EACH OTHER.

32:54.100 --> 32:55.930
SO,IF YOU DIDN'T MEET PEOPLE ONLINE,

32:56.100 --> 33:00.360
