33:01.740 --> 33:05.730
MY WIFE AND I BELONG TO A PRIVATE CLUB CALLED THE VERGE.

33:05.890 --> 33:11.220
IT'S A SPACE ORGANIZED FOR THESE KIND OF...ENCOUNTERS.

33:11.370 --> 33:14.060
