33:19.340 --> 33:21.850
C-CAN YOU TELL ME IF YOU EVER NOTICED

33:22.020 --> 33:25.510
WHAT KIND OF MAN ATTRACTED YOUR WIFE'S ATTENTION?

33:25.670 --> 33:28.150
<i>'CAUSE ONE OF THOSE MEN</i>  <i>MAY HAVE BEEN HER KILLER,</i>

33:28.310 --> 33:30.820
