33:41.250 --> 33:46.270
NAMES?! THERE ARE NO NAMES,OKAY?

33:46.830 --> 33:49.760
ALL RIGHT,YOU WANT EVERY DARK DETAIL. HERE YOU GO.

33:49.910 --> 33:53.590
