34:01.350 --> 34:03.540
THEY HAVE A SPECIAL NIGHT FOR BONDAGE.

34:03.720 --> 34:07.000
SO YOU AND YOUR WIFE HAD SEX AT THE CLUB?

34:07.170 --> 34:09.730
