34:23.239 --> 34:26.130
SOME OF THESE WOMEN ARE FROM OUT OF TOWN AND WILL BE SINGLE.

34:26.300 --> 34:29.190
ALL OUR VICTIMS ARE DIVORCED AND FROM L.A. COUNTY,

34:29.310 --> 34:30.590
SO IT IS REASONABLE TO ASSUME

34:30.750 --> 34:32.550
