34:34.469 --> 34:36.310
IN PROGRESS FOR THIS ROBERT REYNOLDS --

34:36.489 --> 34:38.750
THE AREA BEACHES,THE HIGHWAYS, ALL THE LOCAL MARINAS.

34:38.920 --> 34:41.670
WE ARE STRAINING THE LIMITS OF WHAT COUNTY LAW ENFORCEMENT CAN DO.

34:41.830 --> 34:44.159
BUT OBVIOUSLY,THE KILLER IS CHOOSING HIS VICTIMS IN ADVANCE,

34:44.300 --> 34:47.250
